            <title><![CDATA[【孩子摔倒颅内出血，奶奶：“能不能不拍片，不做检查？”】娃从床上摔下，诊室里医生一摸：“出血了，要拍片。”下一秒，一股火药味蔓延开来——“质疑”医生的...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【孩子摔倒颅内出血，奶奶：“能不能不拍片，不做检查？”】娃从床上摔下，诊室里医生一摸：“出血了，要拍片。”下一秒，一股火药味蔓延开来——“质疑”医生的奶奶：“为啥要拍？不能不拍？”，“哑忍”婆婆的儿媳：“妈，你先别说话。”眼见俩人就要吵起来，医生一句话掐灭“火苗”：必须要拍！看似强硬，实则有医学道理：儿童跌落若有颅内出血，发现不及时分分钟娃就没了。结果一出，一家人都后怕：果然是颅内出血。《闪闪的儿科医生》第二集精彩继续👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E5%84%BF%E5%8C%BB%E9%A6%96%E6%92%AD%E7%BD%91%E5%8F%8B%E7%9B%B4%E5%91%BC%E9%A3%99%E6%B3%AA%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E5%84%BF%E5%8C%BB%E9%A6%96%E6%92%AD%E7%BD%91%E5%8F%8B%E7%9B%B4%E5%91%BC%E9%A3%99%E6%B3%AA%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#闪闪儿医首播网友直呼飙泪#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#闪闪的儿科医生#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4899586779840551" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1hdsevmttz2j21hc0u0n81.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/lOc876olgx085jeVmHWg01041200ClYT0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1683739341&amp;ssig=FAdnJOvRS5&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/xiE9XCe6gx085jeUriuY01041200ku0j0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1683739341&amp;ssig=HADkuM2N5p&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/hxfxyPelgx085jeTOXv201041200dhy50E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkD